# Design system workflow

## Path

`design-system/halisaha/`

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `MASTER.md` | Global rules; **Brand Overrides** section is mandatory |
| `pages/landing.md` | `/` marketing overrides |
| `pages/invite.md` | `/invite/*` fallback overrides |

## Hierarchy

1. Page file (`pages/*.md`) if it exists
2. `MASTER.md` (brand overrides beat generated palettes below)
3. `src/styles/tokens.css` for actual CSS values

## Regenerating (UI Pro Max)

```bash
python3 .cursor/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/scripts/search.py "<query>" \
  --design-system --persist -p "HalıSaha" -f markdown
```

Re-apply **HalıSaha Brand Overrides** in `MASTER.md` after `uipro update` if MASTER was overwritten.

## When to update docs

- New marketing section or page type → add `pages/<name>.md` via `--page`
- Route changes → `docs/architecture.md` + `add-feature-route` skill
